<abstract><t>In the wake of IPv4 exhaustion and deployment of IP address sharing techniques, this document recommends that Internet-facing servers log port number and accurate timestamps in addition to the incoming IP address.  This memo documents an Internet Best Current Practice.</t></abstract>
